---
// IntroSection.astro — story-driven introduction following the hero
---

<section class="intro">
  <div class="intro-inner">
    <div class="eyebrow">A photojournalist&rsquo;s eye. A filmmaker&rsquo;s heart.</div>
    <h2>Stories worth telling. <em>Told well.</em></h2>
    <div class="intro-body">
      <p>
        For twenty years I carried a camera for publications like the
        <i>New York Times</i>, <i>Washington Post</i>, and <i>TIME</i> &mdash; a
        photojournalist trained to find the real stories underneath what people
        say first. The Story Speaks brings that same instinct to brand films,
        documentaries, and impact narratives.
      </p>
      <p>
        Five Emmys, a national Addy, and TED recognition for &ldquo;Ads Worth
        Spreading,&rdquo; I work out of Boulder, Colorado &mdash; partnering
        with mission-driven nonprofits, leading hospitals, research universities, 
        and Fortune 500s across Denver, the Rockies, and the world.
      </p>
      <p>
        No agency bloat. No formula. Just careful storytelling, with a crew
        that scales to fit your project and a budget that respects it
        &mdash; whether you&rsquo;re a global brand, a research institution,
        or a nonprofit fighting for something that matters.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="intro-cta-row">
      <a class="intro-link" href="#films">See the Films &rarr;</a>
      <a class="intro-link" href="#contact">Start a Conversation &rarr;</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .intro {
    background: var(--color-bg-deep);
    background-image: linear-gradient(
      180deg,
      var(--color-bg-deep) 0%,
      var(--color-bg-mid) 100%
    );
    padding: 6rem 2rem 6.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    position: relative;
  }

  .intro-inner {
    max-width: var(--content-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .intro h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.85rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    line-height: 1.12;
    margin: 0 0 2.5rem 0;
    color: var(--color-text);
    text-align: left;
  }

  .intro h2 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .intro-body p {
    font-size: 1.075rem;
    line-height: 1.78;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .intro-body p i {
    font-style: italic;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.96);
  }

  .intro-body p:last-of-type {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .intro-cta-row {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    display: flex;
    gap: 2.25rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .intro-link {
    color: var(--color-text);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 500;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-accent);
    padding-bottom: 6px;
    transition: all var(--transition);
  }

  .intro-link:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    border-bottom-color: var(--color-text);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .intro {
      padding: 4rem 1.5rem 4.5rem;
    }
    .intro-body p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .intro-cta-row {
      gap: 1.25rem;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      margin-top: 2.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>
